WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:28.359
{\an8}There is no deity except You.

00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:29.959
{\an8}Exalted are You.

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:31.720
{\an8}Indeed, I am among the wrongdoers.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:38.079
{\an8}There is no deity but Allah.

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:40.760
{\an8}Muhammad is His messenger.

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:26.119
- Hey, kid, get up. Get up! - Help!

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:28.999
- No! Help! - Come with me!

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:30.880
Help!

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:34.799
Shut up! Silence!

00:01:34.800 --> 00:01:36.759
Hold this girl.

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:37.800
Help!

00:01:48.640 --> 00:01:53.320
- Hey, Sham. Her hand. - Help!

00:01:53.920 --> 00:01:55.119
Her hand, Sham.

00:01:55.120 --> 00:01:57.520
Kid, your hand here... You know, your hand...

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:20.719
I'll slash your hand off.

00:02:20.720 --> 00:02:22.599
Then you'll be crippled.

00:02:22.600 --> 00:02:26.080
Once you're crippled, I'll sell you off.

00:02:33.280 --> 00:02:36.160
Do you hear me? Cry as much as you want.

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:03.239
Where's Dad?

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:05.520
Why aren't you at the hospital?

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:09.120
Do I look like a secretary in this house?

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.839
Why are you being so rude?

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.119
Your dad's in your room.

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:14.959
Ridha.

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:16.799
Your dad's in your room.

00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:19.519
I completely forgot.

00:04:23.880 --> 00:04:24.840
Dad?

00:04:35.880 --> 00:04:37.799
Mom? Mom!

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.559
Quiet!

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:41.759
Mom, why can't I open this door?

00:04:41.760 --> 00:04:44.480
Mom, where's Dad? You said he fell in the bathroom.

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:46.879
Mom.

00:04:46.880 --> 00:04:49.040
Want to know why you're being locked up?

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:53.759
Because you don't give me enough allowance.

00:04:53.760 --> 00:04:57.679
Mom, I give you more than half of what I make.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:58.919
It should be enough.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:00.359
It isn't!

00:05:00.360 --> 00:05:03.959
You should give me every penny of your salary.

00:05:03.960 --> 00:05:06.280
You think you can get away with it because you live on your own?

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:08.479
I can't do that, Mom.

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:10.599
Who'll pay off the two personal loans?

00:05:10.600 --> 00:05:12.839
What a lousy excuse.

00:05:12.840 --> 00:05:15.719
Who told you to take up those loans?

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:17.360
Idiot! Shut up!

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:20.639
I paid for your wedding. Don't you feel ashamed?

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:23.119
Hey, you have to marry Adib

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:24.759
because he promised

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:27.559
to give me 10,000 ringgit

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.320
every single month.

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:34.280
Yes, marry Adib. Serves you right.

00:05:41.720 --> 00:05:43.679
What is wrong with you?

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:45.519
You're trying to sell our daughter.

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:47.799
What's wrong with you? I'm not selling her off.

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:50.319
Even though she's disobedient,

00:05:50.320 --> 00:05:53.559
I still try to find a good husband for her.

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:54.760
You know? So she could live well.

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:58.079
So you think I'm a bad mother?

00:05:58.080 --> 00:06:00.799
Why are you silent? Answer me!

00:06:00.800 --> 00:06:03.600
Am I a bad mother? Oh, gosh.

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:44.319
Megat.

00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.559
Daniel.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:46.560
Take the kids away.

00:07:53.520 --> 00:07:56.240
Well, hello.

00:07:58.120 --> 00:08:02.080
Finally, the sea pups crazed by women are here.

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:05.160
Nice to meet you all.

00:08:05.760 --> 00:08:07.320
The name's Beng.

00:08:09.680 --> 00:08:10.520
Chi Beng.

00:08:12.360 --> 00:08:14.240
Put down all your weapons.

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:18.480
I said, put them down.

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:23.359
One.

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:24.759
He's gone mad.

00:08:24.760 --> 00:08:27.319
Yeah, all bad guys are mad.

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:29.399
Could you just keep quiet?

00:08:29.400 --> 00:08:31.360
Just stand by.

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:33.799
Two.

00:08:34.919 --> 00:08:35.760
Three.

00:08:37.159 --> 00:08:43.079
- Help! - Help us!

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:45.280
- Help! - Help!

00:08:47.320 --> 00:08:48.440
Help!

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:52.319
Help!

00:08:52.320 --> 00:08:55.480
- I learned this from <i>Batman</i>. - Help!

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.040
Inspired by the Joker.

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:00.959
Let go of the kids.

00:09:00.960 --> 00:09:03.520
Sure. I would be happy to.

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:07.000
See that rope?

00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:15.760
I'll see you soon, boys.

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:50.000
Hello?

00:10:12.680 --> 00:10:16.119
Hey, your husband-to-be is here.

00:10:16.120 --> 00:10:17.399
You know what?

00:10:17.400 --> 00:10:20.199
Your groom is tall,

00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:22.799
but his belly is round like Doraemon's.

00:10:22.800 --> 00:10:25.600
He'll surely trip if he walks.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:32.039
No wonder Mom forced you to attend the marriage course.

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:34.200
So she was planning to get you married.

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:40.679
But seriously, your husband is so random.

00:10:40.680 --> 00:10:43.559
He's bald and has a long beard.

00:10:43.560 --> 00:10:45.239
His teeth have gaps.

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:47.199
He wears a robe.

00:10:47.200 --> 00:10:49.880
He must be a pervert.

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:54.279
The marriage solemnizer is on his way.

00:10:54.280 --> 00:10:55.919
Can you wait a bit?

00:10:55.920 --> 00:10:58.719
You must be so eager.

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.520
Bye.

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.800
T.

00:11:14.920 --> 00:11:16.160
H.

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:19.360
A.

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:22.000
R.

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:26.680
I.

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:30.160
Q.

00:11:37.320 --> 00:11:38.400
Peace be upon you.

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:47.280
Did anyone order a ride?

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:05.960
Mom!

00:12:06.760 --> 00:12:08.839
- What's taking you so long? - Stop screaming.

00:12:08.840 --> 00:12:10.799
What's with the shawl and everything?

00:12:10.800 --> 00:12:12.359
- I want to look good. - You do.

00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.359
Peace be upon you too.

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:16.840
Oh, gosh. Please, come in.

00:12:17.680 --> 00:12:19.959
- How are you? - How are you? I'm great.

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:21.360
You look sweet today.

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:29.080
What are you waiting for? Show our son-in-law the place. Go on.

00:12:29.680 --> 00:12:31.399
- Please, do come in. - Yes, come in.

00:12:31.400 --> 00:12:32.799
- Please. - Peace be upon you.

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:34.559
- Peace be upon you too. - Peace be upon you too.

00:12:34.560 --> 00:12:36.319
Great, the solemnizer is here.

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:38.920
- Come, let's go inside. - Come on.

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:41.560
Please open this door.

00:12:44.520 --> 00:12:46.320
I came to save you.

00:12:48.160 --> 00:12:50.239
You think your grand gesture is cute?

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:51.959
You might woo other women,

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:55.519
but honestly, I don't think this is cute at all.

00:12:55.520 --> 00:12:59.040
Yes, I realize that this is totally not cute.

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:02.879
This is the dumbest thing that I have ever done,

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:07.840
but if I have to do this 15 million times, I would.

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:11.520
Because I don't mind being dumb for you.

00:13:14.120 --> 00:13:16.839
- Come. - Go away.

00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:18.839
Come on, I'm already here.

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:21.359
Don't you understand? Go!

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:23.239
So you'll just give in and marry that guy?

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:25.720
It's better than running away with you!

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:32.959
Are you mad at me?

00:13:32.960 --> 00:13:35.559
Mad? I'm no longer upset.

00:13:35.560 --> 00:13:36.919
I just hate you, Ridz.

00:13:36.920 --> 00:13:39.480
I hate you with all my heart!

00:13:45.520 --> 00:13:46.640
I've still got time.

00:14:06.200 --> 00:14:07.600
Honey.

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:25.240
Who is she?

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.320
His fiancée.

00:14:37.520 --> 00:14:39.000
Fiancée?

00:14:40.640 --> 00:14:41.880
Are you serious?

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:49.679
You're going out with me,

00:14:49.680 --> 00:14:51.360
but you got engaged to her?

00:14:53.080 --> 00:14:54.520
Your plot twist is so interesting.

00:15:00.720 --> 00:15:01.640
Let's end this.

00:15:12.920 --> 00:15:14.320
All men

00:15:15.280 --> 00:15:16.720
who have fallen for me

00:15:17.920 --> 00:15:20.080
were all jerks.

00:15:22.560 --> 00:15:24.080
And then you came along.

00:15:25.800 --> 00:15:27.360
I thought you were different.

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:31.600
But it seems that you're even worse.

00:15:40.280 --> 00:15:42.160
Radwa.

00:15:43.080 --> 00:15:44.040
Radwa.

00:15:45.160 --> 00:15:47.560
What? What more do you want?

00:15:48.200 --> 00:15:50.279
I told you before.

00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:52.759
I can only pray and wait for your return.

00:15:52.760 --> 00:15:55.800
Whoever you choose is up to you. It's up to you.

00:15:56.840 --> 00:15:58.360
But remember what you said afterward?

00:15:59.480 --> 00:16:01.800
You would still choose me.

00:16:03.160 --> 00:16:05.039
But you lied, Ridz. You lied!

00:16:05.040 --> 00:16:07.000
- Radwa, I'm sorry. Okay? - Don't!

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:09.880
Don't apologize. It just...

00:16:10.560 --> 00:16:12.240
It just makes it hurt more.

00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:23.720
You deserve better.

00:16:25.200 --> 00:16:26.040
Yeah.

00:16:29.560 --> 00:16:30.520
I know.

00:16:34.400 --> 00:16:35.640
And I agree.

00:16:37.680 --> 00:16:38.760
Let's end this.

00:16:54.320 --> 00:16:56.640
Your dreams have come true.

00:17:00.320 --> 00:17:02.280
Congratulations, Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:17:05.760 --> 00:17:06.920
To me,

00:17:08.839 --> 00:17:11.280
you're dead.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:53.400
Excuse me, sir.

00:17:54.160 --> 00:17:55.720
What are we waiting for? Let's begin.

00:17:57.160 --> 00:18:00.080
But where is the bride?

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:04.240
Yeah, why hasn't she come down?

00:18:05.160 --> 00:18:07.039
How should I know, Mom?

00:18:07.040 --> 00:18:08.920
- This is all your fault. - Why me?

00:18:31.840 --> 00:18:37.480
Gosh! Why are they drilling at a time like this?

00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:57.840
I get that you hate me.

00:18:59.000 --> 00:19:00.759
Thank you for your understanding.

00:19:00.760 --> 00:19:02.240
Now, get lost!

00:19:03.520 --> 00:19:06.080
You can hate me forever, Radwa.

00:19:07.640 --> 00:19:09.840
You still won't be marrying him.

00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:15.599
Hold on. Let me fetch her.

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:18.200
What on earth is she doing up there?

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:23.040
This is embarrassing.

00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:26.760
Let's go.

00:19:35.400 --> 00:19:37.040
Don't regret it.

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:41.920
Or you want to marry him and later regret it.

00:19:42.640 --> 00:19:43.800
Which one?

00:19:45.600 --> 00:19:48.280
Gosh, I didn't unlock it.

00:19:49.080 --> 00:19:54.520
I forgot. How would she get out if it's locked?

00:19:56.240 --> 00:19:57.600
Husniya Radwa.

00:20:48.080 --> 00:20:49.080
Radwa!

00:20:50.760 --> 00:20:51.640
Radwa!

00:20:54.440 --> 00:20:56.919
What is going on? Radwa!

00:20:56.920 --> 00:20:58.199
Hey, Radwa!

00:20:58.200 --> 00:21:00.439
You're getting married. Where are you going?

00:21:00.440 --> 00:21:02.999
I don't mean to disobey you, Mom.

00:21:03.000 --> 00:21:08.039
A useless daughter like you is disobedient or not,

00:21:08.040 --> 00:21:10.279
you belong in one place, hell!

00:21:10.280 --> 00:21:11.639
Where are you going?

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:15.400
I'm sorry, Mom. But I just can't marry him.

00:21:16.360 --> 00:21:17.400
Hey!

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:20.399
I'm sorry, Mrs. Rozita.

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:21.560
Where are you going?

00:21:28.840 --> 00:21:30.399
- Dad. - Radwa.

00:21:30.400 --> 00:21:32.119
Please go with Ridz.

00:21:32.120 --> 00:21:33.559
But I don't want to disobey Mom.

00:21:33.560 --> 00:21:36.079
But if you don't go with Ridz,

00:21:36.080 --> 00:21:37.680
you'll be disobeying me.

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:42.279
- But Mom's... - Who do you love more?

00:21:42.280 --> 00:21:43.439
Me or your mom?

00:21:43.440 --> 00:21:46.840
Go. Hurry.

00:22:03.400 --> 00:22:05.160
So, where to now?

00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:10.600
Swimming in this lake wouldn't be it.

00:22:15.040 --> 00:22:16.240
Radwa.

00:22:21.080 --> 00:22:22.080
Not talking, huh?

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:24.680
Then you can type.

00:22:28.120 --> 00:22:29.160
Okay, fine.

00:22:31.200 --> 00:22:32.320
Let's go to my mom's.

00:22:33.520 --> 00:22:34.560
What's your actual plan?

00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:46.160
Why so hostile? You were nice before.

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:50.600
Nothing's changed.

00:22:51.360 --> 00:22:53.480
Do you think you're Rangga?

00:22:54.640 --> 00:22:55.480
Who's Rangga?

00:22:59.120 --> 00:23:00.600
I'm Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:06.319
Listen, you've taken me away from my home.

00:23:06.320 --> 00:23:08.919
So, what's next? What's your plan?

00:23:08.920 --> 00:23:10.360
I don't know.

00:23:11.360 --> 00:23:12.280
You don't know?

00:23:13.680 --> 00:23:15.479
You should've just left me there.

00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:17.880
No need to play a hero, cutting off the window bars.

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:22.840
- And let you marry that dude? - It's far better than marrying you.

00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:24.280
Oh?

00:23:25.880 --> 00:23:27.320
I never said I'd marry you.

00:23:31.040 --> 00:23:33.879
Always a waste of time. And he kidnapped me.

00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:36.200
What? What am I supposed to do now?

00:24:01.680 --> 00:24:03.880
Lia. Oh, Lia.

00:24:08.080 --> 00:24:09.199
Where have you been?

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:10.799
You called Ridz, didn't you?

00:24:10.800 --> 00:24:12.400
Ridz who?

00:24:15.480 --> 00:24:20.359
Thariq Ridzuwan? Even if you missed him, you shouldn't have pulled my scarf.

00:24:20.360 --> 00:24:21.880
You called him, right?

00:24:22.680 --> 00:24:24.240
Why would I call him?

00:24:24.840 --> 00:24:26.559
To save me from getting married.

00:24:26.560 --> 00:24:28.759
- Getting married? When? With whom? - Adib. This morning.

00:24:28.760 --> 00:24:31.599
- Who's Adib? - The son of my mom's friend.

00:24:31.600 --> 00:24:33.599
Why am I not aware of this Adib?

00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:35.799
We're sisters with different parents.

00:24:35.800 --> 00:24:37.480
How come I didn't know you were getting married today?

00:24:38.560 --> 00:24:40.439
My mom forced me. What else?

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:42.519
She lied, saying that my dad fell in the bathroom.

00:24:42.520 --> 00:24:44.799
So I came home and she locked me up in my room.

00:24:44.800 --> 00:24:46.999
She locked you up? Why didn't you call me?

00:24:47.000 --> 00:24:49.159
I left my phone in the car.

00:24:49.160 --> 00:24:52.200
So Ridz came and saved you from marrying Adib?

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:55.799
He showed up at my window on a crane,

00:24:55.800 --> 00:24:58.079
cut off the window bars, and brought me here.

00:24:58.080 --> 00:25:01.239
Oh, my God. That's so sweet! Do you see his efforts now?

00:25:01.240 --> 00:25:03.519
But how did he find out you were getting married?

00:25:03.520 --> 00:25:04.999
Because you told him.

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:07.520
How could I tell him when I don't even know about it?

00:25:10.640 --> 00:25:13.000
- Then, who called him? - Then, who called him?

00:25:23.680 --> 00:25:24.560
Lia.

00:25:25.800 --> 00:25:26.640
Lia.

00:25:28.800 --> 00:25:29.840
Ridz.

00:25:30.440 --> 00:25:31.760
I know.

00:25:33.560 --> 00:25:35.839
He came back, Lia.

00:25:35.840 --> 00:25:37.760
He showed up in front of me.

00:25:40.160 --> 00:25:41.560
Relax, okay?

00:25:42.840 --> 00:25:44.880
I'm here. It's okay.

00:25:50.440 --> 00:25:51.800
It's okay.

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:09.840
Ridz.

00:26:12.480 --> 00:26:14.000
Do you miss me?

00:26:16.960 --> 00:26:17.960
No.

00:26:18.600 --> 00:26:20.840
You're so funny.

00:26:21.680 --> 00:26:22.800
No, I'm not.

00:26:34.400 --> 00:26:39.200
I came here to fulfill a promise.

00:26:40.280 --> 00:26:41.240
What promise?

00:26:44.680 --> 00:26:46.800
I promised Aina

00:26:48.200 --> 00:26:50.280
that when she turns 25

00:26:51.240 --> 00:26:53.520
and you're still single,

00:26:54.120 --> 00:26:56.640
I want you to marry Aina.

00:27:02.040 --> 00:27:05.359
That's a big smile.

00:27:05.360 --> 00:27:08.719
I'm sure that means you're happy to marry Aina.

00:27:08.720 --> 00:27:10.240
No.

00:27:11.440 --> 00:27:12.960
Just a bit entertained.

00:27:14.400 --> 00:27:16.160
You're so funny.

00:27:17.840 --> 00:27:20.840
What does your promise to Aina have to do with me?

00:27:21.400 --> 00:27:23.080
Please don't create drama.

00:27:25.360 --> 00:27:27.280
Why won't you marry her?

00:27:28.360 --> 00:27:31.520
I've liked you since I was little.

00:27:32.120 --> 00:27:34.600
Yeah, because you were always hanging around here.

00:27:35.640 --> 00:27:37.440
I take you as my sister.

00:27:38.400 --> 00:27:40.960
But not an actual sister.

00:27:41.840 --> 00:27:43.719
By religion,

00:27:43.720 --> 00:27:46.120
you're allowed to marry Aina.

00:27:47.240 --> 00:27:48.240
Auntie.

00:27:50.800 --> 00:27:53.040
Can you stop talking about us getting married?

00:27:53.680 --> 00:27:57.119
My hand might not know how to shake your hand in the future.

00:27:57.120 --> 00:27:59.399
Why is it so hard for you to accept her?

00:27:59.400 --> 00:28:00.800
Listen here.

00:28:02.960 --> 00:28:04.720
My life partner,

00:28:05.360 --> 00:28:08.240
my soulmate, is the one and only

00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:11.160
Husniya Radwa.

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:13.040
No one else.

00:28:14.160 --> 00:28:17.519
She's my past, present, and future.

00:28:17.520 --> 00:28:19.160
That is my vow.

00:28:22.560 --> 00:28:23.839
If you'll excuse me.

00:28:23.840 --> 00:28:25.280
Peace be upon you.

00:28:34.440 --> 00:28:36.159
What should we have for lunch?

00:28:36.160 --> 00:28:37.999
Smashed chicken.

00:28:38.000 --> 00:28:40.119
- Sounds good, right? - The sambal is to die for.

00:28:40.120 --> 00:28:41.560
I think...

00:28:48.520 --> 00:28:52.600
Radwa.

00:28:55.840 --> 00:28:57.200
Are you okay?

00:28:59.520 --> 00:29:00.959
Are you okay?

00:29:00.960 --> 00:29:04.520
I was worried. I've never heard from you since that day.

00:29:05.320 --> 00:29:10.640
I was worried you might get sick or something.

00:29:11.480 --> 00:29:15.800
I called you so many times, but I couldn't reach you.

00:29:16.960 --> 00:29:19.200
I left my phone in my car, Mom.

00:29:21.360 --> 00:29:22.920
I know.

00:29:25.040 --> 00:29:27.679
So today, I came here with your dad.

00:29:27.680 --> 00:29:30.520
I want to return your car.

00:29:32.360 --> 00:29:34.440
I've parked it at the front.

00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:38.240
One more thing.

00:29:43.160 --> 00:29:44.320
Your cellphone.

00:29:46.680 --> 00:29:49.160
I've charged it for you.

00:29:50.320 --> 00:29:53.319
From now on, if I call you,

00:29:53.320 --> 00:29:54.360
can you please answer?

00:29:56.160 --> 00:29:57.520
Promise?

00:30:06.160 --> 00:30:08.079
You were supposed to get married last Saturday.

00:30:08.080 --> 00:30:10.599
But why did you run off with another guy?

00:30:10.600 --> 00:30:12.880
Why?

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:16.559
The solemnizer was there. Preparations were done.

00:30:16.560 --> 00:30:20.200
The groom was there. How could you do that to me?

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:26.239
Now, I want you to feel my embarrassment.

00:30:26.240 --> 00:30:28.719
Mrs. Rozita, Radwa has the right to marry--

00:30:28.720 --> 00:30:29.959
Shut up!

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:31.800
Shut up. Not a word from you.

00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:37.279
Adib asked for 50,000 ringgit as compensation.

00:30:37.280 --> 00:30:40.160
You have to pay for that. If you don't, you'll be sued.

00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:44.919
If you don't want to see your dad and me get locked up,

00:30:44.920 --> 00:30:46.760
pay that compensation.

00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:53.800
Where are we going to get 50,000?

00:30:54.680 --> 00:30:59.879
50,000. You have to pay for that. If you don't pay, you'll be sued.

00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:05.160
Breathe. Breathe.

00:31:08.520 --> 00:31:10.000
It's okay.

00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:13.039
<i>Sorry, Niya.</i>

00:31:13.040 --> 00:31:15.240
Your application didn't go through.

00:31:15.880 --> 00:31:17.400
Your credit score failed.

00:31:19.400 --> 00:31:22.240
I've been making monthly payments, Sara.

00:31:22.840 --> 00:31:24.719
But it was rejected by the system.

00:31:24.720 --> 00:31:25.800
What more can I do?

00:31:27.360 --> 00:31:29.239
I'm sure there's a way you can help me.

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:31.760
Niya, my KPI is being evaluated.

00:31:32.360 --> 00:31:34.359
You're a high-risk borrower.

00:31:34.360 --> 00:31:36.119
I'll get in trouble.

00:31:36.120 --> 00:31:37.520
High risk?

00:31:39.080 --> 00:31:42.119
When you were down and had no sales,

00:31:42.120 --> 00:31:45.279
you begged me to take a personal loan from you, so I helped.

00:31:45.280 --> 00:31:47.879
Even when your bank's interest was over the roof,

00:31:47.880 --> 00:31:49.599
I still took out two loans under you.

00:31:49.600 --> 00:31:51.759
Niya, if you weren't sincere,

00:31:51.760 --> 00:31:54.440
you shouldn't have helped, okay?

00:31:54.960 --> 00:31:56.800
You don't need to bring that up.

00:32:01.960 --> 00:32:04.439
You are just like your system.

00:32:04.440 --> 00:32:05.720
Cruel capitalists.

00:32:06.320 --> 00:32:07.400
Cruel.

00:32:14.960 --> 00:32:17.199
Guys, she said I was cruel.

00:32:17.200 --> 00:32:18.439
So rude.

00:32:18.440 --> 00:32:21.360
- What? - Oh, my God. How rude.

00:32:22.680 --> 00:32:24.320
I really hate Niya.

00:32:25.160 --> 00:32:27.120
Why don't we take revenge on her?

00:32:28.720 --> 00:32:29.599
But how?

00:32:29.600 --> 00:32:32.040
We prank her like we used to.

00:32:32.560 --> 00:32:36.039
But what kind of prank are we going to do?

00:32:36.040 --> 00:32:37.679
I have an idea.

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:40.479
What if we invite her to the reunion

00:32:40.480 --> 00:32:43.839
and embarrass her in front of everyone?

00:32:43.840 --> 00:32:45.399
Like the good old times.

00:32:45.400 --> 00:32:47.280
I don't think she'll come.

00:32:48.360 --> 00:32:49.639
She's desperate for money, right?

00:32:49.640 --> 00:32:54.000
We'll announce that there'll be a lucky draw at the reunion.

00:32:54.600 --> 00:32:57.080
The winner shall receive 50,000 ringgit.

00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:59.760
- How does that sound? - That's right.

00:33:00.360 --> 00:33:02.159
Serves her right.

00:33:02.160 --> 00:33:03.800
Oh, Niya.

00:33:05.360 --> 00:33:09.320
I, Datin Zizi Abu Samah,

00:33:09.880 --> 00:33:12.519
as the benefactor of the Teduh Transit Home,

00:33:12.520 --> 00:33:17.160
hereby declare Teduh Library officially open for the children.

00:33:25.560 --> 00:33:26.960
Where is it?

00:33:27.720 --> 00:33:29.600
- Where's what, sweetheart? - My present.

00:33:33.040 --> 00:33:35.320
You used to remember my birthday.

00:33:39.640 --> 00:33:42.960
Never mind. I'm not sad.

00:33:45.080 --> 00:33:50.080
<i>- May God bless you - May God bless you</i>

00:33:50.760 --> 00:33:56.359
<i>- May God bless you - May God bless you</i>

00:33:56.360 --> 00:34:01.639
<i>- May God bless you, Fateh</i> - Come on.

00:34:01.640 --> 00:34:05.640
<i>- May God bless you - May God bless you</i>

00:34:09.719 --> 00:34:11.480
Thanks, Wawa.

00:34:15.239 --> 00:34:17.678
You can hate me a million times over,

00:34:17.679 --> 00:34:19.920
but don't let Fateh miss out on a gift because of me.

00:34:20.639 --> 00:34:23.159
Take this. Please.

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:26.360
Take it.

00:34:30.600 --> 00:34:32.719
- Happy birthday, Fateh. - Thank you.

00:35:14.600 --> 00:35:17.960
You don't need to pretend to be an introvert by standing here by yourself.

00:35:21.240 --> 00:35:22.120
Is that for me?

00:35:23.720 --> 00:35:25.960
Is this what you call love?

00:35:37.400 --> 00:35:39.520
Husniya Radwa.

00:35:42.960 --> 00:35:43.840
Radwa.

00:35:44.520 --> 00:35:49.320
I've been meaning to ask you this.

00:35:52.400 --> 00:35:54.720
Your name is Husniya Radwa, right?

00:35:56.000 --> 00:35:58.519
But has anyone ever called you,

00:35:58.520 --> 00:36:01.720
"Bro, one Husniyarawatusu, please!"

00:36:07.120 --> 00:36:09.400
You haven't changed even a bit.

00:36:22.920 --> 00:36:24.520
Five years, Thariq.

00:36:25.520 --> 00:36:28.120
You disappeared for five years, then you popped up out of the blue.

00:36:28.720 --> 00:36:30.239
What are you hoping for?

00:36:30.240 --> 00:36:32.120
Not to marry me, right?

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:34.800
So where's your fiancée?

00:36:35.720 --> 00:36:37.720
Or has she been bombed to death?

00:36:39.880 --> 00:36:42.919
You don't even know the difference between a landmine and a pot.

00:36:42.920 --> 00:36:45.119
- How'd you get into the army? - I no longer have a fiancée.

00:36:45.120 --> 00:36:46.080
Why?

00:36:47.000 --> 00:36:48.599
Why do you want to know?

00:36:48.600 --> 00:36:51.759
Don't be cheeky by answering a question with a question.

00:36:51.760 --> 00:36:53.280
I'm not flirting with you.

00:36:58.480 --> 00:36:59.679
Radwa.

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:03.200
This is not the Radwa I knew. Why are you so mad at me?

00:37:03.720 --> 00:37:07.360
The Radwa you knew never liked people who easily got upset.

00:37:07.880 --> 00:37:11.120
You're the reason I hated myself.

00:37:13.960 --> 00:37:16.600
I had no one else at the time, Ridz.

00:37:17.720 --> 00:37:19.719
I only had you.

00:37:19.720 --> 00:37:22.280
I was depending only on you.

00:37:23.080 --> 00:37:25.359
But you lied to me.

00:37:25.360 --> 00:37:28.120
You left me for another woman.

00:37:29.560 --> 00:37:31.799
Until I felt numb.

00:37:31.800 --> 00:37:33.759
Yes, I did want to die.

00:37:33.760 --> 00:37:36.760
But I didn't even have the guts to die.

00:37:37.400 --> 00:37:38.960
I was an idiot, wasn't I?

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:41.000
Weak.

00:37:43.120 --> 00:37:47.480
So I bottled up all that pain until eventually I became angry.

00:37:48.080 --> 00:37:51.239
I didn't like it, but that was the only way I knew how to cope,

00:37:51.240 --> 00:37:52.679
so I didn't lose my mind.

00:37:52.680 --> 00:37:56.159
- Radwa, you-- - I was filled with anger, Ridz.

00:37:56.160 --> 00:37:58.959
Radwa, you can't be like this forever.

00:37:58.960 --> 00:38:00.680
Please don't do this.

00:38:01.800 --> 00:38:05.119
Teduh is the only place I can calm down.

00:38:05.120 --> 00:38:07.240
Even for a moment.

00:38:07.840 --> 00:38:09.919
Only by being here, I don't think of you,

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:13.040
I forget you, and I don't feel like I've lost my mind.

00:38:13.880 --> 00:38:15.879
- But you still ruined it. - Husniya Radwa.

00:38:15.880 --> 00:38:17.839
Why do you hate me so much?

00:38:17.840 --> 00:38:21.600
Why can't you leave me alone in peace?

00:38:23.600 --> 00:38:26.439
Why can't you stop hurting me?

00:38:26.440 --> 00:38:29.279
I never meant to hurt you, Radwa.

00:38:29.280 --> 00:38:31.760
As long as you're around,

00:38:33.160 --> 00:38:36.040
I keep hurting.

00:38:40.600 --> 00:38:43.720
I hate you, Ridz.

00:38:48.520 --> 00:38:49.920
I hate you.

00:39:21.560 --> 00:39:23.599
You were so late.

00:39:23.600 --> 00:39:26.840
The store was about to close. Luckily, the lady was nice.

00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:29.919
There are only a few days left.

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:32.120
Where can I dig up the money to pay Adib?

00:39:36.600 --> 00:39:38.679
I know.

00:39:38.680 --> 00:39:41.159
- I can borrow from loan sharks. - Hey.

00:39:41.160 --> 00:39:44.519
No. No, Husniya Radwa.

00:39:44.520 --> 00:39:45.959
Don't do it.

00:39:45.960 --> 00:39:48.320
Lia, this is my only chance.

00:39:51.120 --> 00:39:52.639
Hey.

00:39:52.640 --> 00:39:55.080
The reunion! There'll be a lucky draw.

00:39:55.760 --> 00:39:56.599
So?

00:39:56.600 --> 00:39:59.720
If you win, you'll get 50,000 ringgit.

00:40:00.640 --> 00:40:01.880
So?

00:40:02.600 --> 00:40:05.160
Just go and try. Who knows? You might win.

00:40:06.520 --> 00:40:07.759
That's ridiculous, Lia.

00:40:07.760 --> 00:40:11.199
Who in their right mind would donate 50,000 for a college reunion?

00:40:11.200 --> 00:40:14.239
Unless it's the Megah Holdings Annual Dinner.

00:40:14.240 --> 00:40:17.959
Just give it a whirl. You might win. Just show up, Niya.

00:40:17.960 --> 00:40:20.920
Just imagine. One hundred people attend the event.

00:40:21.880 --> 00:40:23.559
Only one can win the lucky draw.

00:40:23.560 --> 00:40:25.519
Just in case you haven't noticed, my life is full of bad luck.

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:26.879
I'll never win these things.

00:40:26.880 --> 00:40:29.239
Come on, just come with me.

00:40:29.240 --> 00:40:31.199
Rather than borrowing money from loan sharks,

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:33.439
it's better to attend the reunion.

00:40:33.440 --> 00:40:35.359
Okay, listen.

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:36.319
Just show up.

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:41.039
If you don't win, you can borrow from loan sharks or whoever you want.

00:40:41.040 --> 00:40:43.639
But I promise you that during your funeral,

00:40:43.640 --> 00:40:46.039
you won't have your hands and feet anymore.

00:40:46.040 --> 00:40:47.600
And my speech will be like this,

00:40:48.720 --> 00:40:51.440
"The deceased was a total idiot."

00:40:53.520 --> 00:40:55.319
Your ideas are nonsense.

00:40:55.320 --> 00:40:57.079
Is my dress all right?

00:40:57.080 --> 00:41:00.440
We'll talk about the 50,000 later. Just make sure you go, okay?

00:41:04.800 --> 00:41:06.559
<i>Wa, where are you? Are you coming?</i>

00:41:06.560 --> 00:41:08.719
It's about to start.

00:41:08.720 --> 00:41:10.359
I hate her for doing this.

00:41:10.360 --> 00:41:12.480
Hey, Dahlia.

00:41:13.720 --> 00:41:15.120
What do you want?

00:41:16.880 --> 00:41:17.920
Is Niya coming?

00:41:18.880 --> 00:41:20.000
What's it to you?

00:41:21.960 --> 00:41:24.720
She's not coming to the reunion because of me, right?

00:41:25.960 --> 00:41:27.599
Listen up, Syafiq.

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:30.799
Niya accepted you before out of pity.

00:41:30.800 --> 00:41:34.079
She didn't know how to reject you. Why?

00:41:34.080 --> 00:41:36.239
She's afraid you'd get sulky.

00:41:36.240 --> 00:41:41.319
And when that Medusa or Maria stole you from her,

00:41:41.320 --> 00:41:42.959
did you see her lose her mind?

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:45.039
No, right?

00:41:45.040 --> 00:41:46.440
What's his problem?

00:41:47.480 --> 00:41:50.920
Honey!

00:41:51.440 --> 00:41:56.239
Dahlia. Happy to see you here.

00:41:56.240 --> 00:42:00.480
- Lia! Oh, my God! We miss you! - Lia!

00:42:01.400 --> 00:42:02.519
- Where's Niya? - Where's Niya?

00:42:02.520 --> 00:42:04.440
Why is everyone so interested in her?

00:42:12.720 --> 00:42:13.760
Guys.

00:42:14.880 --> 00:42:17.999
- So Niya isn't coming? - She will.

00:42:18.000 --> 00:42:21.400
She's desperate to win that 50,000, isn't she?

00:42:22.200 --> 00:42:25.479
Hi, good evening, boys and girls.

00:42:25.480 --> 00:42:27.839
Look at me here. Hi!

00:42:27.840 --> 00:42:31.239
This year, we're going to have a big surprise!

00:42:31.240 --> 00:42:33.000
A big round of applause.

00:42:36.520 --> 00:42:40.599
This year, we'll be doing a lucky draw.

00:42:40.600 --> 00:42:45.240
The winner shall receive 50,000 ringgit.

00:42:51.600 --> 00:42:54.079
Sara. Please, come over here.

00:42:54.080 --> 00:42:55.679
It's time to draw the name.

00:42:55.680 --> 00:42:57.960
Who do you guys think the winner is?

00:43:01.280 --> 00:43:03.559
And the winner is...

00:43:03.560 --> 00:43:05.359
Drum roll!

00:43:05.360 --> 00:43:08.720
Husniya Radwa!

00:43:15.280 --> 00:43:17.639
Niya, where are you?

00:43:17.640 --> 00:43:19.639
You've won yourself 50,000 ringgit.

00:43:19.640 --> 00:43:21.559
Fifty thousand.

00:43:21.560 --> 00:43:24.719
I have a really great prize for you, Niya.

00:43:24.720 --> 00:43:27.399
Husniya! Or...

00:43:27.400 --> 00:43:28.560
Here.

00:43:30.280 --> 00:43:33.039
So there's our winner.

00:43:33.040 --> 00:43:35.079
Where did you go, Niya? Hurry up.

00:43:35.080 --> 00:43:36.719
Come on, you won.

00:43:36.720 --> 00:43:39.360
Niya, hurry. You won. Don't you want the prize?

00:43:42.800 --> 00:43:45.279
Congratulations!

00:43:45.280 --> 00:43:47.799
Take a step forward. All right.

00:43:47.800 --> 00:43:50.719
{\an8}- A big round of applause. - Over here.

00:43:50.720 --> 00:43:53.400
One, two, three. Smile!

00:44:06.160 --> 00:44:07.759
Serves you right.

00:44:07.760 --> 00:44:10.760
This is the greatest prize for Niya.

00:44:12.720 --> 00:44:14.080
Niya.

00:44:36.600 --> 00:44:42.160
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

00:44:49.760 --> 00:44:51.920
{\an8}<i>When will you get it through your head</i>

00:44:53.560 --> 00:44:56.320
{\an8}that you're the reason behind my pain?

00:44:57.520 --> 00:44:58.959
{\an8}This is Zafir.

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:01.359
{\an8}He just came back from the States.

00:45:01.360 --> 00:45:05.480
{\an8}Soon, you two will get engaged.

00:45:07.000 --> 00:45:09.520
{\an8}Stop! Stop!

00:45:11.200 --> 00:45:14.320
{\an8}Let me take care of you every moment of the day.

00:45:15.560 --> 00:45:19.839
{\an8}Can I trust that you won't leave me like you once did?

00:45:19.840 --> 00:45:22.759
{\an8}I think it's time for Radwa to know

00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:25.399
{\an8}why you had to leave her before.

00:45:25.400 --> 00:45:28.280
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

